This Hazara boy?

955
01:24:47,560 --> 01:24:48,880
Yeah.

956
01:24:50,079 --> 01:24:51,920
What he means to you?

957
01:24:54,199 --> 01:24:57,840
His father meant a lot to me.
He's the man in the photo.

958
01:24:59,199 --> 01:25:00,800
He's dead now.

959
01:25:02,039 --> 01:25:03,920
lt was a friend of yours?

960
01:25:05,560 --> 01:25:07,000
