You come here to rescue a boy.

1015
01:29:13,279 --> 01:29:16,040
take him back to America.
give him a good life.

1016
01:29:16,840 --> 01:29:18,920
lt must seem heroic. huh?

1017
01:29:19,560 --> 01:29:21,760
